      <div>
        <h4>The Problem</h4>
        <p>
            While Skullcandy’s <a href="https://skullcandy.com">current website</a> has well-designed graphics with an engaging use of color, it lacks a design that speaks to the outdoor actions sports demographic that is considered to be their target audience. This inconsistent messaging is hindering Skullcandy’s ability to create a memorable brand that the target audience chooses when shopping for new audio products.
        </p>
        <h4>Objectives</h4>
        <p>
            The goal of this website redesign was to infuse more of the brand’s history into its product promotion. The story of Skullcandy’s inception should be used to connect with the target audience and show how the products are designed specifically for them. The following are metrics that will be used to determine the success of this website redesign
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Increase in online sales.</li>
          <li>
            Increase in average time on website.
          </li>
          <li>Increase in repeat visits.</li>
        </ol>
