      <h4>Target Audience</h4>
      <p>
        Company founder and former CEO Rick Alden has noted that Skullcandy was created for the skateboarder, snowboarder, surfers, and those that want a reliable way to listen to their music while they live an active lifestyle. 
      </p>
      <p>
        There are a few things to consider when thinking about the target audience's perspective on purchasing audio products:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          There are so many options in the market that potential customers may not know what the best option is to fit their needs.
        </li>
        <li>
          A quality set of headphones or earbuds tend to be relatively expensive, and since Skullcandy's target demographic is people that live an active lifestyle, they know their headphones/earbuds may need to be replaced more frequently. Because of this, they are wanting something that is more affordable.
        </li>
        <li>
          The target customer would prefer to go to a store and try on a bra to
          ensure the correct size is purchased.
        </li>
      </ol>
  
